    <string name="module1_1_1_title">ALPHABET AND STRINGS</string>
    <string name="module1_1_1_content_1">In this lesson, we\'ll dive into the foundational concepts of
alphabets and strings, essential building blocks in the study of formal languages and computational
theory. An alphabet is a set of symbols, and a string is a sequence of these symbols. Understanding these
basics is crucial as they form the basis for more complex topics such as languages, grammars, and
automata that will be covered in future lessons.</string>
