    <string name="module1_1_7_title">Reversal of Strings:</string>
    <string name="module1_1_7_content_1">The reversal of a string w, denoted wR

, is the string

obtained by reversing the order of its symbols.</string>
    <string name="module1_1_7_content_2">Example: If w = "abc", then wR

= "cba".</string>

